an 500 mm on the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_4675f7a8-6558-4f69-a7a5-72f7c1ad1464" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> width (including any landings) of a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_8afdcb45-7c54-492a-b6d3-5251f8d9cbf8" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> stairway, ramp or passageway if it is likely to impede the path of travel of the people already using the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_6f065b04-b259-4b73-bd1f-8ce1607a1cd1" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref>; and</li><li>when fully open, by more than 100 mm on the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_4b892f9d-460b-4834-914e-3e8050cd83de" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> width of the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_a9ad4ea6-7655-4fbb-b626-07f67b26c199" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_c764dc15-194d-4ff0-b80e-04dc004453b8" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref>; and</li></ol></li><li id="_3c31eb39-ce3a-4bd9-b4f5-4087b033aa77">must swing in the direction of egress unless—<ol><li>it serves a building or part